---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Nav from '../components/Nav.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  lang="en"
  title="Privacy Policy | GymAI Club"
  description="GymAI Club privacy policy."
>
  <Nav lang="en" />
  <main class="info-page wrap">
    <section class="info-hero">
      <div class="sec-kicker">PRIVACY POLICY</div>
      <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p></p>
    </section>

    <section class="info-card legal" aria-label="Privacy policy content area">
      <div class="legal-updated">Last Updated: July 6, 2026</div>

      <p>At GymAI Club ("the App"), we care about your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains what data we collect while you use the App, how we use it, and your rights.</p>

      <h2>1. Data Controller</h2>
      <p>This App is developed and operated by independent developer <strong>Onur Küçüktürk</strong>. For privacy-related questions, you can reach us at <a href="mailto:gymaiclub01@gmail.com">gymaiclub01@gmail.com</a>.</p>

      <h2>2. Data We Collect</h2>

      <h3>2.1 Account Information</h3>
      <p>When you sign in via your Google or Apple account, we receive basic identity information (name, email address, profile photo). This information is used only to create your account and verify your identity.</p>

      <h3>2.2 Camera Data</h3>
      <p>The App requests access to your device's camera to analyze your movement form. This analysis is performed <strong>entirely on-device</strong>; your camera footage is never transmitted to or stored on our servers.</p>

      <h3>2.3 Photo Gallery</h3>
      <p>Access to your gallery is requested so you can choose a profile photo. The photo you select is used only to display on your profile.</p>

      <h3>2.4 Health and Fitness Data (Apple HealthKit)</h3>
      <p>If you grant permission, your workout progress and daily activity may be shared with the Apple Health app. This data is used solely to provide you with a personalized workout experience and is never used for advertising or marketing purposes, nor shared with third parties.</p>

      <h3>2.5 AI-Powered Features</h3>
      <p>The App uses a third-party AI service provider (Anthropic) to generate personalized workout plans and recommendations. Data transmitted in this process is processed solely to provide you with the service.</p>

      <h3>2.6 Usage Data</h3>
      <p>Basic technical data (device model, OS version, app version, crash reports) may be collected to ensure the App functions properly.</p>

      <h2>3. Data We Do Not Use</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>We do not use any advertising or tracking SDKs</strong> (e.g. Facebook SDK, AdMob).</li>
        <li>We do not collect or use your device's Advertising Identifier.</li>
        <li>We do not collect your location data.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>4. Data Sharing</h2>
      <p>Your personal data is not shared with third parties except in the following cases:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Where required by legal obligation</li>
        <li>With subprocessors necessary to provide the service (e.g. cloud infrastructure providers), limited strictly to operating the service</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>5. Data Security</h2>
      <p>Your data is protected with industry-standard security measures (encrypted connections - HTTPS). However, please note that no transmission over the internet is 100% secure.</p>

      <h2>6. Data Retention and Deletion</h2>
      <p>You can permanently delete your account at any time via <strong>Settings → Delete Account</strong> within the App. Once your account is deleted, your associated personal data is removed from our systems.</p>

      <h2>7. Children's Privacy</h2>
      <p>The App is not intended for individuals under the age of 18. We do not knowingly collect data from users we know to be under 18.</p>

      <h2>8. Your Rights</h2>
      <p>Regarding your personal data, you have the right to:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Request access to your data</li>
        <li>Request correction of your data</li>
        <li>Request deletion of your data</li>
      </ul>
      <p>You can submit these requests to <a href="mailto:gymaiclub01@gmail.com">gymaiclub01@gmail.com</a>.</p>

      <h2>9. Changes to This Policy</h2>
      <p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you within the App in the event of significant changes.</p>

      <h2>10. Contact</h2>
      <p>For questions about this Privacy Policy: <strong><a href="mailto:gymaiclub01@gmail.com">gymaiclub01@gmail.com</a></strong></p>
    </section>
  </main>
  <Footer lang="en" />
</BaseLayout>
